  <h3>Surficial Geology Map</h3>
  <p>
    I will spend my first Alaskan winter sifting through IFSAR data to map
    surficial geology in the Malaspina region of the park. Maybe one day there
    will be a complete surficial geology map of the park, but we've got to start
    somewhere!
