  <h3>...and more!</h3>
  <p>
    I am assisting with the design of physical models to be used in visitor
    displays and outreach. The models will be of the Kennicott and Tyndall
    glacier valleys with removable ice surfaces from different points in history
    for comparison between different glacier types and rates of ice retreat.
  </p>
